  [2]: https://github.com/google/diff-match-patch/wiki/Language:-Java
  [3]: https://github.com/java-diff-utils/java-diff-utils
  [4]: https://code.google.com/archive/p/java-diff-utils/
  [5]: https://github.com/java-diff-utils/java-diff-utils/wiki/Examples
  [6]: https://www.techiedelight.com/implement-diff-utility/
  [7]: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Longest_common_subsequence_problem
  [8]: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Levenshtein_distance
  [9]: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edit_distance

